Class CHPReseqForceCall

java.lang.Object
  affymetrix.calvin.data.CHPReseqForceCall

public class CHPReseqForceCall
extends java.lang.Object

A structure to hold a force call, its position and reason. A force call is the call the algorithm would have made if the thresholds were not applied.
